The,SmartRecruiters,Marketplace,API,allows,developers,to,incorporate,their,apps,into,the,SmartRecruiters,staffing,platform,The,API,provider,SmartRecruiters,Inc,offers,customers,a,suite,of,proprietary,personnel,recruitment,solutions,Developers,using,the,RESTful,API,can,select,all,or,either,of,the,three,builder,platforms,that,is,Offer,Assessment,and,Job,Board,APIs,that,have,varying,HR,recruitment,management,functionalities,depending,on,the,type,of,corresponding,marketplace,services,The,SmartRecruiters,Marketplace,API,is,already,out,as,a,well,documented,full,release,version,that,requires,token,authorization,for,access,Its,responses,to,requests,are,formatted,in,JSON